Officially starting an ethnic wear brand that I’ve always dreamed about💕Go follow @doriva.in 💖

My vision is simple:
Unique, elegant Desi pieces, consciously made in limited drops

Me and my mom wanted to start this a while ago, but life kept getting in the way
Now, with the support of both my mom and sister, I finally pushed through and made it happen🧿

I really hope you all will love what we’ve been creating 🪡
and I’d be so grateful for your support
This means the world to me🤍
